title: Spliced Business Formations Within 4 Quarters for Wyoming (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Business Formation Statistics are now released on a monthly basis, and the quarterly series will no longer be updated. See BFSBF4QTOTALSAWY (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFSBF4QTOTALSAWY) for an alternative.

This series combines (splices) https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BF4QSAWY and https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/PBF4QSAWY to provide the entire time series for the actual and projected business formations within 4 quarters.
